# 🛡️ V-Watch Edge AI System

An AI-powered **real-time traffic surveillance system** using YOLO, DeepSORT tracking, and violation detection (speeding, red light, lane violations, ANPR).

---

# 🚀 Features

* 🚗 Real-time vehicle detection (YOLOv8)
* 🎯 Multi-object tracking (DeepSORT)
* ⚡ Speed estimation system
* 🚦 Red-light violation detection
* 🛣️ Wrong-direction & lane violation detection
* 🔍 Automatic number plate recognition (ANPR)
* 📸 Evidence generation (image + video clips)
* 🌐 Backend API integration
* 🐳 Fully Dockerized system
* 🎥 Live camera / RTSP / video file support

